jMath.linalg
Class Vector

java.lang.Object
  jMath.linalg.Vector

public class Vector
extends java.lang.Object

The class Vector represents an n-dimensional vector. Intentionally mimics many of the naming conventions of MATLAB.

Version:
April 1, 2010
Author:
S. Andrew Ning
